\par }{\i\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid14187295\charrsid14187295 Is it a corner we've turned and no coming back? }{\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid14187295\charrsid14187295 Lizbeth wondered.
