\par "If you're sure."
\par "I'm sure."
\par "Say, why are we so interested in that embryo?"
\par "You don't need to know, sweetie.\~ Get back to work and let me get some sleep."
\par She broke the connection, still wondering about the noise she had heard.\~ It had sounded like something being hit.
\par Allgood sat staring at the blank screen after the nurse signed off.\~ }{\i\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid14187295\charrsid14187295 Noise?\~ Commotion?\~ }{\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid14187295\charrsid14187295 
