\par "Go down to that vat room and inspect it," Allgood said.\~ "The fine tooth.\~ Look for signs of a commotion."
\par "But if anybody sees us --"
\par "Damn it to hell!\~ Do as I say!"
\par "Yes, sir!"
\par The agent clicked off.
