\par Boumour shrugged.\~ "Well, we expect to loose a certain percentage."
\par "My wife is not a }{\i\insrsid14187295 certain percentage," }{\insrsid14187295 Harvey growled.\~ He turned, focused a glare on Boumour that sent the man retreating three steps.
