\par }{\i\insrsid14187295 "They }{\insrsid14187295 have sealed us in here," Glisson said.\~ Again, that sing-song twang as though something about him had been broken.\~ "As you can see, I am dis-armed.\~ Do you not think that amusing?\~
 Do you see now why we could never fight }{\i\insrsid14187295 them }{\insrsid14187295 openly?\~ When they wish it, they can destroy anything .\~.\~. anyone."
