\par }{\i\insrsid14187295 We made no plans for the unthinkable, }{\insrsid14187295 she thought.\~ }{\i\insrsid14187295 Is it possible that this nobody who was once a target for kindly sneers can save us?\~ }{\insrsid14187295 She dared not let herself hope.

