. zest for life, this excitement you prize."
\par "You propose to make of us living }{\i\insrsid14187295 vats for embryos?" }{\insrsid14187295 Calapine asked, wonder in her voice.
\par "The gestation process can be delayed for hundreds of years," Svengaard said.\~ "With proper hormone adjustment, this can be applied even to men.\~ Caesarian delivery, of course, but it need not be painful .\~.\~. or frequent."
