\par }{\i\insrsid14187295 This is politics, }{\insrsid14187295 she thought.\~ }{\i\insrsid14187295 This is the way the Tuyere would do it .\~.\~. even Schruille.\~ Especially Schruille.\~ Clever Schruille.\~ Dead Schruille.\~ }{\insrsid14187295 
